{{mid}}
*German: [[sich]] [[verlieben]]
*Italian: [[innamorarsi]]
*[[Novial]]: [[ameska]]
*Polish: [[zakochać się]]
*Portuguese: [[apaixonar-se]], [[enamorar-se]]
{{bottom}}

'''of two people'''
{{top}}
